title: Net Change in Corporate Securities Outstanding, Stock, All Industries for United States
notes:
Data Represent The Difference Between Data In Series (New Corporate Securities Issued, Stocks, All Industries) And Series 10123 (Corporate Securities Retired, Stocks, All Industries.) Source: Securities And Exchange Commission, For 1948-1959 Data: Unpublished Table, April 1, 1959; For 1960-1964 Data: Sec Statistical Bulletin

This NBER data series q10124 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 10 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter10.html.
